8d1b33eb7527daf2ee6ff5df62ef1","tid":1166528,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T14:30:37.000Z","msg":"16.04？<br />\n19.04都出咗喎"},{"pid":"12b6335e0fc1232603fd79ab8a885b39a513690d","tid":1166528,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:24:20.000Z","msg":"留俾愛國人士選購 , 真貼心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544a5a4db6684b62f6b1f3832a07c3ac9bc7e876","tid":1166528,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經諗好左將來無windows要點生存<br />\n係linux裝android模擬器, 以後只打手機game, 之後用brower上網<br />\n文書就用office 365 subscription, 有online版word excel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e384d70b88e5b8b97e1769435bb5cbf30099ea68","tid":1166528,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"544a5a4db6684b62f6b1f3832a07c3ac9bc7e876","tid":1166528,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經諗好左將來無windows要點生存<br />\n係linux裝android模擬器, 以後只打手機game, 之後用brower上網<br />\n文書就用office 365 subscription, 有online版word excel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:30:35.000Z","msg":"新版 Steam Play 介紹<br />\n2018 年 8 月 21 日 下午 2:40\t<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/games/221410/announcements/detail/1696055855739350561?l=tchinese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fgames%2F221410%2Fannouncements%2Fdetail%2F1696055855739350561%3Fl%3Dtchinese&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTS195pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=91809177\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcommunity.com/games/221410/announcements/detail/1696055855739350561?l=tchinese</a><br />\n<br />\n兩年前我們便著手改善 Steam 遊戲的 Windows 相容性解決方案之品質與效能。我們在支援 Wine[<a href=\"http://www.winehq.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.winehq.org&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTS195pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=f5ec86d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.winehq.org</a>] 和其他既存的相容性專案上花了很多功夫，也在持續把這些工具整合進 Steam 用戶端，希望 Steam 能像許多 Linux 的普通遊戲一樣，提供簡簡單單隨插即玩的體驗。<br />\n<br />\n我們的目標是讓 Linux Steam 使用者能輕鬆存取更多過去的產品。我們認為開發人員也能利用這些成果，未來能夠輕鬆地把產品從其他平台搬移至 Linux，同時也能選擇把精力投注於其他方面，像是支援 Vulkan[<a href=\"http://www.khronos.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.khronos.org&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTS195pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=20c293c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.khronos.org</a>] 這種對所有使用者的經驗而言更具意義的議題。<br />\n<br />\n我們今天將分享目前的工作成果，發表改良過後的新版 Steam Play 的測試版，供所有 Linux 使用者使用。此測試版包含了名為「Proton」的 Wine 分發修改版，可為 Windows 遊戲產品提供相容性。以下是一些我們完成的改良：<br />\n<br />\n目前尚<span style=\"color: red;\">不支援 Linux 的 Windows 遊戲現在能安裝並可直接於 Linux Steam 用戶端中運作</span>，帶原生 Steamworks 與 OpenVR 支援，更加完整。<br />\n<br />\nDirectX 11 與 12 實作現在以 Vulkan 為基礎，改善了遊戲相容性並減少效能影響。<br />\n<br />\n改善全螢幕支援：可配合選定的螢幕完美調整全螢幕遊戲，不干擾原生螢幕解析度，無需使用虛擬桌面。<br />\n<br />\n改善遊戲控制器支援：遊戲會自動辨識所有 Steam 支援的控制器。即買即用的盒裝控制器相容性提升，甚至可能比原版遊戲的支援更加優秀。<br />\n<br />\n多執行緒遊戲之效能相較一般的 Wine 大幅提升。"},{"pid":"6f161ca010754815660082a05279033c2fccf7f6","tid":1166528,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8963090db34ec121f0684502f944005e7eac1937","tid":1166528,"uid":146604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:55:09.000Z","msg":"買黎format完自己裝window都幾低玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adc7c78a87ac60692172626e60b5a158b77ddf7","tid":1166528,"uid":41308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:59:36.000Z","msg":"班癈佬港女師9貪平買左番黎<br />\n<br />\n一開機，大叫「乜野黎?無windows既。點鬼識用」<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔計android 未用過Linux"},{"pid":"da9f50f1ccf0922d2422a8c415889a097bf9d0b3","tid":